|B'C'|=\alpha|BC|
\Delta A'B'C'
\text{area}(\Delta A'B'C')=\frac1{2}|A'B'||B'C'|=\frac1{2}k\alpha |AB||BC|.
\text{area}(\Delta A'B'C')=\text{area}(\Delta ABC)+\text{area}(\Delta CEC')+\text{area}(BCDB')
=\frac1{2}|AB||BC|+\frac{1}{2}|CD||DC'|+|BC||BB'|.
|CD|=|BB'|=|A'B'|-|AB|=(k-1)|AB|\text{ , and}
|DC'|=|B'C'|-|BC|=(\alpha-1)|BC|.
\text{area}(\Delta A'B'C')=\frac1{2}|AB||BC|+\frac1{2}(k-1)|AB|(\alpha-1)|BC|+(k-1)|AB||BC|.
\frac1{2}k\alpha |AB||BC|=\frac1{2}|AB||BC|+\frac1{2}(k-1)|AB|(\alpha-1)|BC|+(k-1)|AB||BC|,
\Rightarrow k\alpha =1+(k-1)(\alpha-1)+2(k-1),
\Rightarrow k\alpha=1+\alpha k-k-\alpha+1+2k-2,
\Rightarrow \alpha=k\,\,\,\bullet
\Delta ADE\sim \Delta BDF
|AD|=k|BD|\text{ and }|DE|=k|BF|,
\Rightarrow \frac{|AD|}{|BD|}=\frac{|DE|}{|BF|}\,\,(**).
|AE|^2=|AD|^2+|DE|^2\text{ and }|CE|^2\underset{(*)}{=}|BD|^2+|BF|^2,
\Rightarrow \frac{|AE|^2}{|CE|^2}=\frac{|AD|^2+|DE|^2}{|BD|^2+|BF|^2}\underset{(**)\text{ and Lemma 2}}{=}\frac{|AD|^2}{|BD|^2}\,\,\bullet
